reviewText: excellent can't wait until I get the next season of my all time favorite shows thanks alot
I'm not a deadliest catch fan and it was a gift to my now ex. The dvds came nicely packaged and wrapped.

I watched them all totally entertaining I thought It was Great very informative I learned a lot about what it takes to do what they do its unbelievably amazing! I definitely Highly recommend this to anyone who is contemplating that occupation and anyone who loves the sea and fishing LOL!
I just love teh Deadliest Catch & to be able to have the shows right at my fingertips any time I want, is wonderful. With the After The Catch  shows also included in the DVD sets, is an added bonus
this was and is a great buy, hours of one of my favorite shows to watch over and over. I had also purchased Mama's Family you talk about a dispointment my gosh. worst purchase from amazon.
